snippet.title: Sonic: Edge of Darkness - SAGE 2014 Act 2 Demo Release Trailer
snippet.description:
It's that time of the year again, and Edge of Darkness is back with new Acts and a brand new Zone! Adventure through three levels as either Sonic, Tails, or Knuckles, and take on Robotnik & Metal Sonic! Demo available August 3rd, 2014.

SAGE Website:
http://sagexpo.org/

Our Page:
http://sagexpo.org/games/sonic-edge-of-darkness/
